    public class PreviewFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    PreviewFrame determines an application for exporting and previewing a video file from an archive of SVG animation slices.

        public static void showHelp​(java.lang.String helpSetName,

        Requests that the given help section ID from the given help set be displayed in the ModelEditor's help viewer.
        Parameters:
        helpSetName - a String containing the HelpSet name. For example: SNAP for the SNAP ModelEditor help set. For the english locale this will be interpreted as i18n/en/SNAP.
        sectionName - a String containing the section ID of the topic to display.
